Package: joker
Type: Package
Title: Return a Random Joke from APIs
Version: 0.0.3
Authors@R: c(person("Tan", "Ho", email = "tan@tanho.ca",role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Jeffrey W Hollister",role = c("aut")),
             person("Mathias Schilling", role = c("cph")),
             person("Antoine Bichat",role = c("ctb")),
             person("Brett Langdon", role = c("cph")))
Description: What is funnier than a joke?  A joke in R!  This package 
    utilizes the APIs for <https://icanhazdadjoke.com> and <https://chucknorris.io> and returns a random
    dadjoke or Chuck Norris joke.
